query.sparql: SELECT (GROUP_CONCAT(?answer; separator=', ') AS ?answer) ?count WHERE { SELECT DISTINCT ?answer (COUNT(?answer) AS ?count) WHERE { <https://dblp.org/rec/journals/toit/LybackB04> <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#authoredBy> ?x . ?x <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#primaryAffiliation> ?answer } GROUP BY ?answer } ORDER BY DESC(?count) LIMIT 1
